{"tid":1598411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平:堅決打擊民族分裂活動，實現中華民族偉大復興","createTime":"2019-09-27T12:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:05:34.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"888b5fdabbd15d21abe6628c2b851aafbf8cedcc","tid":1598411,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2261548/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3:%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2261548%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%3A%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=b3dd9c3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2261548/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3:%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95</a><br />\n<br />\n國家主席習近平在北京舉行的全國民族團結進步表彰大會上強調，中國特色社會主義進入新時代，中華民族迎來歷史上最好的發展時期。同時，面對複雜的國內外形勢，更要團結一致、凝聚力量。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他指出，實現中華民族偉大復興，需要各民族共同努力奮鬥。要以鑄牢中華民族共同體意識為主線，全面貫徹黨的民族理論和民族政策，堅持共同團結奮鬥、共同繁榮發展，把民族團結進步事業作為基礎性事業抓緊抓好，促進各民族像石榴籽一樣緊緊擁抱在一起，推動中華民族走向包容性更強、凝聚力更大的命運共同體。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又強調，要依法治理民族事務，確保各族公民在法律面前人人平等。要全面貫徹落實民族區域自治法，依法保障各民族合法權益。要依法妥善處理涉民族因素的案事件，保證各族公民平等享有權利、平等履行義務，確保民族事務治理在法治軌道上運行。對各種滲透顛覆破壞活動、暴力恐怖活動、民族分裂活動、宗教極端活動，要嚴密防範、堅決打擊。"},{"pid":"91546246c4fee357f8c1c786a008d01aeb4d4e26","tid":1598411,"uid":118322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"民族主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2357d1d87ce6f6cb65fc39ee8606e03550dfbb","tid":1598411,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:25:57.000Z","msg":"民族分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db908648b7bf66f00e7ce06b534a4932cec061db","tid":1598411,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:26:51.000Z","msg":"noted"},{"pid":"8227c50b0f6032db6525fc388696637e6c175405","tid":1598411,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e13849f61463b9a71cffc0359dd0bd085e3212","tid":1598411,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"幾時出兵收復蒙古<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ab5b2d890f68093105c17550e5522a976149b3","tid":1598411,"uid":189224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"合久必分，分久必合，民族特色嚟架喎"},{"pid":"b57e5640d1003cfde2fec24492d3da041a281b4d","tid":1598411,"uid":210121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"支爆近了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44af51caae45ee07ee292d9ffade136f3efed6bb","tid":1598411,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e13849f61463b9a71cffc0359dd0bd085e3212","tid":1598411,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"幾時出兵收復蒙古<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"等佢出兵收服香港等到瞓著左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536886ef97fc37be471770c8ba430bedeb0a4f9e","tid":1598411,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44af51caae45ee07ee292d9ffade136f3efed6bb","tid":1598411,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e13849f61463b9a71cffc0359dd0bd085e3212","tid":1598411,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci